      • getStorageUnitNotificationRegistrationKeysByNotificationFilter

        List<NotificationRegistrationKey> getStorageUnitNotificationRegistrationKeysByNotificationFilter(StorageUnitNotificationFilter storageUnitNotificationFilter)
        Gets a list of keys for all existing storage unit notification registrations that match the specified storage unit notification filter parameters.
        Parameters:
        storageUnitNotificationFilter - the filter for the storage unit notification. Only the following four filter parameters are used to match the storage unit notification registrations:

        • the namespace of the business object definition (required, case-insensitive)
        • the name of the business object definition (required, case-insensitive)
        • the usage of the business object format (optional, case-insensitive)
        • the file type of the business object format (optional, case-insensitive)
        Returns:
        the list of storage unit notification registration keys

      • getStorageUnitNotificationRegistrations

        List<StorageUnitNotificationRegistrationEntity> getStorageUnitNotificationRegistrations(String notificationEventTypeCode,
                                                                                        BusinessObjectDataKey businessObjectDataKey,
                                                                                        String storageName,
                                                                                        String newStorageUnitStatus,
                                                                                        String oldStorageUnitStatus,
                                                                                        String notificationRegistrationStatus)
        Retrieves a list of storage unit notification registration entities that match given input parameters.
        Parameters:
        notificationEventTypeCode - the notification event type code (case-insensitive)
        businessObjectDataKey - the business object data key (case-insensitive)
        storageName - the name of the storage (case-insensitive)
        newStorageUnitStatus - the new storage unit status (case-insensitive)
        oldStorageUnitStatus - the old (previous) storage unit status (case-insensitive). This parameter will be null for storage unit creation
        notificationRegistrationStatus - the status of the notification registration (case-insensitive)
        Returns:
        the list of storage unit notification registration entities
